Notes: The CEA service area includes: Beluga, Cooper Landing, Girdwood, Hope, Moose Pass, Point Possession, Sunrise and Tyonek.
In addition to Valdez, the CVEA service areas includes 14 communities.
In addition to Fairbanks, the GVEA service are includes 25 communities.
